Package: inventory
Type: Package
Title: Computation of Optimal Reorder Points
Version: 0.2.1
Authors@R: person('Dennis', 'Malandro',
    email = 'dennismalandro@gmail.com', role = c('aut', 'cre'))
Description: Fit lead-time and demand-rate nonparametric density
    estimates.  Integrate conditonal lead-time density over
    demand-rate density to get the marginal lead-time demand
    distribution.  Integrate this in turn to get the 
    reorder-point/service-level relationship.
